data.description: Conveniently located 4 bedroom 2 bath home newly painted exterior is waiting for you to move in. There is ample room to move and store  your belongings. There is a one car garage and also a carport. The backyard has a patio area and a shed with a concrete floor with electric. Enjoy the charm of a century home with today's amenities. Forced air gas heating with central air, a main floor bath and main floor laundry. Right in the heart of the city close to shopping, restaurants and grocery stores.
